ein|Thörl]]'' || ''Terle''{{listref|D}} || Slovenian: ''Vrata'' |- | ''[[Tröpolach]]'' || ''Trepule''{{listref|D}} || Slovenian: ''Dropolje''{{listref|E}} |- | ''[[Villach]]'' || ''Vilac''{{listref|D}} || Slovenian: ''Beljak''{{listref|E}} |- | ''{{illm|Warmbad Villach|de|Warmbad-Judendorf}}'' || ''Bagns di Vilac''{{listref|D}} || Slovenian: ''Toplice pri Beljaku |- | ''{{illm|Würmlach|de|Würmlach|it|Würmlach}}'' || ''Virmule'' || Slovenian: ''Bumlje'' |- |}
